{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-11", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "立場不同", "storyInfo": "為獲取關於薩卡茲補給線的情報，羅德島與自救軍聯軍對城防軍指揮塔發起進攻。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "9:37 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆奧克特里格區，城防軍總指揮塔附近"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島阿米婭特別行動隊的幹員們，按照計劃，我們即將配合自救軍，對倫蒂尼姆城防軍指揮塔展開突襲行動。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的目標只有一個，取得城防系統中關於薩卡茲補給線的資訊記錄。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這份資訊將影響我們整個倫蒂尼姆行動的成敗。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管......我們很可能已經來不及阻止特雷西斯向大公爵們宣戰。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果能得到這份情報，我們將有機會延緩戰爭的步伐，儘量減少戰爭帶來的犧牲。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們盡可能做了許多準備，可仍有許多突發情況是無法預料的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們心中都很清楚，接下來的戰鬥，只會一場比一場艱難。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們走到這裡，都是為了同一個目標，一個不會動搖的目標。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該繼續前進了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，還有一種突發情況。;還有一位薩卡茲的王可能出現在戰場上。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line48", "option2": "line48"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我知道你在擔心我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能說自己一定準備好了......可自從離開薩迪恩區，我設想過許多遍下一回再見到她的情形。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她站在我們的對面，我很想知道她這樣做的原因。我想感受......她所感受到的一切。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但就像我對幹員們說的那樣，我絕不會忘記我們來到這裡的初衷。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很清楚，特蕾西婭小姐所希望的薩卡茲和整片大地的未來正在離我們遠去。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的未來，正是我和凱爾希醫生，還有每一個跟著我們一同進入倫蒂尼姆的幹員渴望抓住的未來。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為此，我們做好了迎接一切可能性的準備，也會像最後一戰一樣拼盡全力。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那出發吧。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line63"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，博士，我們出發。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g7_controltower", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的軍隊最近調動得很快。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，中校。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近大家都說......都說......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說薩卡茲馬上就要和公爵部隊開戰了。到時候，他們會把我們做成血肉傀儡，扔到戰場上去。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，中校。說這些違背了您制定的紀律。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不怪你們。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們相信您，中校。我們都知道與薩卡茲交涉有多艱難......但您做到了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些年裡，是您帶著我們走過了那麼多險境。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯塔福德公爵叛亂那次也是，要不是您的準確判斷，我早就死在了叛軍的炮火下！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您一次次救了我們，也一次次在不同野心家的手裡保住了這座城市。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要是您做的決定，我們都不會質疑。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是因為我知道......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.8}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armycrowd", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$calamity_intro", "key": "$calamity_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下面街道上什麼聲音？", "nam