 {"content": "——早上好。", "name": "維多利亞雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這些人是從哪裡冒出來的？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別問了，除非你願意花很多錢。", "name": "維多利亞雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵......你們是誰派來的？哪位大公爵？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不認識任何大公爵。他們更不可能認識我們。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......你們是反抗軍？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自救軍......自救......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很清楚這是為什麼。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本該與薩卡茲戰鬥的人是你們。你們選擇了投降，那我們